      "description": "## Korean Movie Search v1.0.0\n\nInitial release of the Obsidian plugin that automatically fetches Korean movie information.\n\n### Features\n- Movie metadata search via KOBIS (Korean Film Council) API\n- Poster images and ratings via TMDB API integration\n- Bilingual UI support (Korean / English)\n- Customizable frontmatter fields\n\n### Install\nCopy `main.js`, `manifest.json`, and `styles.css` to your vault's `.obsidian/plugins/korean-movie-search/` folder.",
